{"word":"πορνεύω","slug":"πορνεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πορνεύω</b></el> <el>(πορνεύω,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to prostitute</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, of a woman, <i>to be</i> or <i>become a prostitute</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a>, = <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:πόρνη'><el>πόρνη</el></a>\n"}]}